QuestData.Title: Ending Executions
QuestData.Description: We arrived as soon as we could... but we be too late. Da Iron Horde has taken our warriors prisoner.$b$bNo doubt they be trying ta squeeze info out of da troops.$b$bI fear once they are done with da interrogation they gonna execute their prisoners. Time be running out.
QuestData.RewardText: Da prisoners be shaken up, but they are free. We be in your debt, $n.
